        name: 'Joel Shebioba',
        job: 'OL (GB Lions + Postdam Royals)',
        image: {
          src: '~/assets/images/IMG-20250813-WA0006.jpg',
          alt: 'Joel Shebioba',
        },
      },
      {
        testimonial: `Having never played football before uni, the brilliant coaching mixed with the playful environment of the team led me to pursue further education on a scholarship, as well as with playing professionally abroad. The best decision I've made in my life was to join the club.`,
        name: 'Gabriele Battistella',
        job: ' DB (Milano Seamen + ifm Razorbacks)',
        image: {
          src: '~/assets/images/IMG-20250813-WA0007.jpg',
